pointing to a news conference in Washington on Monday.
   Terry Lierman, a Washington lobbyist who founded the group, said
the organization will not lobby Capitol Hill, but instead take its
message _ with Weicker as the point man _ around the country to
educate the public and rally citizens' support to put additional
pressure on Congress.
